You can ovverrid a `resolve_` method for your `SQLAlchemyConnectionField` and apply desired filters

```python
class Something(SQLAlchemyObjectType):
    class Meta:
        model = SomethingModel

class Query(graphene.ObjectType):
    something = SQLAlchemyConnectionField(Something)
    
    def resolve_something(self, args, context, info):
        query = Something.get_query(context)
        return query.filter(SomethingModel.user_id == authenticated_user.id)
```

